  CONV_TAC (DEPTH_CONV patternMatchesLib.PMATCH_ELIM_CONV)
  \\ Cases_on ‘v’ \\ Cases_on ‘ps’ \\ simp [SmartMat_def]
  \\ rename [‘(h::t)’]
  \\ PairCases_on ‘h’ \\ rpt CASE_TAC \\ simp [SmartMat_def]
QED

